      &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Update, 3:42 p.m., 6/20/24:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Earlier today, Ubisoft accidentally posted a trailer for Beyond Good &amp;amp; Evil – 20th Anniversary Edition alongside news the game would be coming to all platforms next week. However, shortly after, it deleted the post. Now, Ubisoft has reposted the news, confirming Beyond Good &amp;amp; Evil – 20th Anniversary Edition is, in fact, real and launching on PlayStation, Xbox, Switch, and PC on June 25.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Check out the trailer for yourself in the announcement below&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;


